Steps to set Language Pack in magento 2

1) Download Language pack
2) CLI >> php bin/magento info:language:list (Find Your Language pack code)
3) CLI >> php bin/magento setup:static-content:deploy <Language_Code>
4) CLI >> php bin/magento setup:upgrade
5) CLI >> php bin/magento setup:static-content:deploy
6) Admin >> store >> cofiguration >> general >> general >> Locale Options >> Set your language as Locale
7) Save Config
8) set Static string in different language >> set in  echo __(<string>); 
9) copy string and set in CSV(language pack)

